{
  "texts": [
    "An example is shown in Figure 1.",
    "• Comprehensive assessment.",
    "AdvancedIF contains 1,600+ prompts including three important aspects of instruction following: (b) Multi-turn instruction following: the ability to follow instruction carried from previous; and (c) System prompt steerability: The ability to follow instructions in the system prompt.",
    "• Challenging benchmark.",
    "We benchmark SoTA LLMs such as GPT5, Gemini 2.5 Pro, and Claude-4-Sonnet, the best result achieved by them is around 70%, which shows IFAdvanced is quite challenging and can better reflect the gap between existing LLMs and the north star."
  ]
}